t: 37*400=14800, 37*16=592, sum=15392. 15397-15392=5. Not divisible.\n- 41: 41*300=12300. 15397-12300=3097. 41*70=2870. 3097-2870=227. 41*5=205, remainder 22. 41*375=15375. 15397-15375=22. Not divisible.\n- 43: 43*300=12900. 15397-12900=2497. 43*50=2150, 2497-2150=347. 43*8=344, remainder 3. 43*358=15394? 43*358 = 43*300 + 43*58 = 12900 + 2494 = 15394. Remainder 3.\n- 47: 47*300=14100. 15397-14100=1297. 47*20=940, 1297-940=357. 47*7=329, remainder 28. 47*327=15369? 47*327 = 47*300 + 47*27 = 14100 + 1269 = 15369. Remainder 28.\n- 53: 53*300=15900 (too high). 53*290=15370. 15397-15370=27. Not divisible.\n- 59: 59*200=11800. 15397-11800=3597. 59*60=3540. 3597-3540=57. 59*260=15340, remainder 57. Not divisible.\n- 61: 61*200=12200. 15397-12200=3197. 61*50=3050, 3197-3050=147. 61*2=122, remainder 25. 61*252=15372. 15397-15372=25.\n- 67: 67*200=13400. 15397-13400=1997. 67*25=1675. 1997-1675=322. 67*5=335 (too high), 67*4=268. 322-268=54. 67*229=15343? Let's compute 67*230 = 15410. 15410-15397=13. Not divisible.\n- 71: 71*200=14200. 15397-14200=1197. 71*10=710, 1197-710=487. 71*6=426, remainder 61. 71*216=15336? 71*217 = 15336+71=15407 >15397. Not divisible.\n- 73: 73*200=14600. 15397-14600=797. 73*10=730, remainder 67. Not divisible.\n- 79: 79*200=15800 >15397. 79*190=15010. 15397-15010=387. 79*4=316, remainder 71. 79*194=15326? 79*195=15405. Not divisible.\n- 83: 83*180=14940. 15397-14940=457. 83*5=415, remainder 42. 83*185=15355. 15397-15355=42.\n- 89: 89*170=15130. 15397-15130=267. 89*3=267 exactly? 89*3=267! Yes! 89*3=267.\nSo 15397 = 15130 + 267 = 89*170 + 89*3 = 89*173.\nThus 15397 is divisible by 89. (89*173 = 15397? Let's check: 90*173=15570, minus 173 = 15397. Correct.)\nSo 15397 is NOT prime.\n\nAnswer: 15397 is not prime; it is 89 × 173.", "content_starved": false, "finish_reason": "stop", "verdict": "correct", "extracted": false, "extraction_source": "reasoning", "format_flags": {"chars": 3468, "refusal_marker": false, "has_markdown": true, "verbose": true}, "